AVSQpvpgZqV-OukZKKADeN7bB_479YeInj-mEpmtnQcg&oe=671E1C94"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "coverImage2560.png", "id": "1171525093276710", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982681_1171525096610043_1669834911006050355_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5oParwwGCawQ7kNvgGGhs6_&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDxGS7iTBt4LfdGAm5B84dxDokADo1OtQmzpbfSxe-G5A&oe=671E2F06"}, "display_name": "Dogfight Elite", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Embark on an exhilarating journey through history with Dogfight Elite, a thrilling combat simulator set against the monumental backdrop of World War I and II.\n\nBecome the master of the skies in Dogfight Elite. Commandeer the cockpit of a warplane, spearhead a tank into battle, or bravely face the enemy on foot as a resilient soldier. The battlefield has never felt this real and the stakes this high.\n\nTest your mettle in solo play, navigating through meticulously designed training missions that escalate to adrenaline-charged, full-scale aerial dogfights against relentless enemy combatants.\n\nWhile Dogfight Elite is free-to-play, opting for a subscription unlocks a treasure trove of exclusive benefits. Take to the skies or the battlefield with premium airplanes, tanks, and specially-crafted weapons, and embark on captivating, subscriber-only missions.\n\n\nMoreover, subscribing allows you instant access to our servers and priority queuing, ensuring that your historic battles remain uninterrupted. Experience the past like never before with Dogfight Elite - the battlefield is waiting for you.\n\nIf you have any requests/complaints please visit www.dogfightelite.com forums.\nI keep track of all requests and complaints and fix them on each release. Write the details or contact me on the website. I will read your posts and fix it asap!", "short_description": "Online massive airplane combats against real pilots, tanks, and foot soldiers."}]},